{"tid":2029521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我必須學習政治和戰爭，這樣我的兒子就有可能自由地去學習數學和哲學。為左下一代, 大家係時候團結一致","createTime":"2020-05-22T09:20:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T15:04:50.000Z","uid":19817,"like":79,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"aac5bd7cafc3a8f0fc4a4e71decc9bccd2e46108","tid":2029521,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T09:20:21.000Z","msg":"最大既暴風雨終於來臨<br />\n<br />\n我地要用盡一切方法去延續香港既精神<br />\n<br />\n手足講得好岩, 香港唔係一個地方, 香港係一種精神, 呢種精神只有真正當呢度係屋企既人先會有<br />\n<br />\n呢種意識係有生命力, 係打不死<br />\n<br />\n我地冇受過仇恨教育, 並唔係因為仇恨而抗爭, 我地只係受正義受道德感召而企出黎<br />\n<br />\n又或者叫嫉惡如仇<br />\n<br />\n今日開始我地既教育系統已經唔再存在, 聽日開始我地獲取資訊既渠道亦都可能唔再存在<br />\n<br />\n個世界唔知會變成點, 全方位去裝備去鍛鍊自己, 全方位去學習你以前討厭既野,<br />\n<br />\n去保護我地既下一代, 直到呢場暴風雨結束<br />\n<br />\n令到革命之火可以延續落去, 歷史唔係係書入面, 歷史永遠係人既心裡面<br />\n<br />\n多用鼓勵方式對自己人, 唔好成日鬥呢樣果樣, 敵人就係用呢種方式去攻陷我地既世界<br />\n<br />\n團結一致, 只為八隻字<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港, 時代革命</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UeWkY6W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUeWkY6W.jpg&h=9915349f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6125081c499df29be491947461ed6ef5354bfecf","tid":2029521,"uid":1989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T09:27:47.000Z","msg":"極權不亡 抗爭不休<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ab11fef3d3e4af6f7c855dfd31395560a3bbd62","tid":2029521,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T09:30:41.000Z","msg":"但那裡可以學到軍事呢？"},{"pid":"28d2372e8b99cecf359889fcf342079f49b16504","tid":2029521,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6125081c499df29be491947461ed6ef5354bfecf","tid":2029521,"uid":1989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T09:27:47.000Z","msg":"極權不亡 抗爭不休<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T09:31:02.000Z","msg":"浴火重生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a52b6682caaf1a5b8f31fa4d5fb27e26481f2f0","tid":2029521,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ab11fef3d3e4af6f7c855dfd31395560a3bbd62","tid":2029521,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T09:30:41.000Z","msg":"但那裡可以學到軍事呢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T09:32:58.000Z","msg":"全方位鍛鍊同學習左知識先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f94b59327a9a7db2e97c4b307f8896c44a9f4cc","tid":2029521,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T09:33:43.000Z","msg":"下一代唔學政治、戰爭，就會做港豬。<br />\n做港豬都冇問題，最怕日後又有極權劏港豬嘅時候，港豬根本唔識、冇決心反抗。"},{"pid":"b50a0dd7180781c2068a423ba3f37df080d7f97f","tid":2029521,"uid":253016,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T09:33:54.000Z","msg":"香港既垃圾廢老就係貪圖逸樂先會累而家我地受到折磨"},{"pid":"57fbd8a8a795b8f990866ad24b47b08eeecc7c0a","tid":2029521,"uid":120913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T09:34:42.000Z","msg":"唔推post正hihi<br />\n我們都是香港之子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c22e4f1f83f90dd32e328f6e0b0fab7e959c896b","tid":2029521,"uid":75664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T09:35:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"189de046e68983a26a5ac18351f803fae27148e4","tid":2029521,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T09:46:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f95d29021f801102b6d5d04db874c2d2c991af2d","tid":2029521,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b50a0dd7180781c2068a423ba3f37df080d7f97f","tid":2029521,"uid":253016,"l